<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.SetAllocationFunction" Title="SetAllocationFunction method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin">IRendererPlugin</PageRef> ->
    SetAllocationFunction
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetAllocationFunction</TypeRef> method sets the function pointer used to allocate a graphics device enumerator for this renderer plugin.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[virtual void SetAllocationFunction(AllocatorPointer allocator) = 0;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="AllocatorPointer!cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.AllocatorPointer" Name="allocator">
          The allocator function exported by the renderer plugin implementation.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
